# Launcher: exclude the whole directory from Tailwind v4's content scanner
# (Tailwind honours .gitignore). Without this, incidental strings in
# launcher/*.ts are picked up as utility candidates and leak unused rules into
# the app CSS bundle, changing the GitHub Pages build output. The launcher
# TypeScript sources ARE version-controlled — they are committed with
# `git add -f`; only the build artifacts (embedded.generated.ts, icon.ico) are
# genuinely untracked.
# NOTE: a NEW launcher source file must be staged with `git add -f launcher/…`;
# a plain `git add` will skip it because of this rule.
launcher/
